      • getTransactionsToString

        public java.lang.String getTransactionsToString(java.lang.String addTitleTabs,
                                                java.lang.String addContentTabs)
        Reveal details of all the transactions in this Stock, sorted by TimeStamp:

        Old is presented below, and New is presented above.

        For each transaction show:

        • TimeStamp.
        • quantity of sold stocks.
        • price of selling.
        • transaction's period.
        Note: if there were'nt any transactions with this Stock, return a message.
        Parameters:
        addTitleTabs - add here the amount of 'tab's to insert before the Title.
        addContentTabs - add here the amount of 'tab's to insert before the Content.
        Returns:
        String of all the Transactions of this Stock.
